						 <p>Heyo!<br /> Throw the confetti! Lay the red carpet, for the post is here!<br /> Finally got around to this tale staring your everyday Alagadda news, please enjoy yourselves!</p> <p>The image provided is made by yours truly, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5963620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598484902" alt="Luxaiko" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5963620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" >Luxaiko</a></span>. And the formatting was all done with the help of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598484902" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598484902" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598484902" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.co